# orb-common (Python)

Shared types and utilities for the orb ecosystem.

## Installation

```bash
pip install orb-common
```

For CodeArtifact installation, see [docs/common-library.md](../../../docs/common-library.md).

## Usage

```python
from orb_common import EnvironmentDesignator

# Use enum directly
env = EnvironmentDesignator.DEV
print(f"Deploying to {env}")  # "Deploying to dev"

# Parse from string (case-insensitive)
env = EnvironmentDesignator.from_string("DEV")

# Get all valid values
values = EnvironmentDesignator.values()  # ["dev", "stg", "uat", "qa", "prd"]
```

## Development

```bash
# Install dev dependencies
pipenv install --dev

# Run tests
pipenv run pytest tests/ -v

# Run type checker
pipenv run mypy orb_common/

# Run tests with coverage
pipenv run pytest tests/ --cov=orb_common --cov-report=term-missing
```
